Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come one, come all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:04.94,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Cigarettes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shells for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:07.44,MX Handwritten - 20yen1,,0000,0000,0000,,20\Nyen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:13.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His place should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure to find him today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of spending the night at campsites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.70,MX Handwritten - 20yen2,,0000,0000,0000,,20 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:21.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:23.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shells for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:24.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.38,Tattoo Dog 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so competitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:39.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing shop keeper, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:45.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You like children?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For publicity's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty nasty guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dislike them, Kawafuji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:56.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd come to like her, \Ngiven another ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not liking children, that's liking women.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I prefer mature women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:04.89,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:05.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck, now my hand's slimy! It's filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to break my glasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You dig it out with a needle like this, and eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.63,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,*Good children boil them before eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ick ick ick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:16.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does someone named Handa \NSeishuu live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:20.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:22.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seishuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:24.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:25.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:26.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a Sensei who goes \Nby a stylish name like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:30.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:31.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our penmanship teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:35.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Handa-sensei's house is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:38.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you buy a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Very shrewd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sell me that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have fine judgment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:50.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can only sell this to someone wealthy, \Nlike an eye-tea company head or major leaguer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:52.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you accept this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much are you willing to sell for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I want you to show me the way, I'll splurge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:02.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a deal at a million yen, you thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a deal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time seein' one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:13.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:14.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:18.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the way to—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm gonna show this to Gramma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! This comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take me—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you guys from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:31.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatchin' a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:38.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the fire brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a village meetin' now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't ya come tell us all 'bout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:45.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji-san!
