Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.99,Barakamon Title Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Translation: \NGuys From Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for this food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:32.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you guys \Neating dinner at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and Mom went to the community \Ncenter for the village meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's tastier than when eating alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:40.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer eating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:48.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you've gained weight \Nsince you came to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The languid country air is ruining me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man oughta be a little plump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've been wondering \Nabout this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this scribbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.03,Tattoo Dog 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I met a fella with scribblin' on his arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:11.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scribbling"? Isn't that a tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower and "Dog" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.33,Tattoo Dog 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these round things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate Marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:20.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the guy's tattoo a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all muddled up, so I couldn't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've gotten a number \Nof texts since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:35.02,Phone Names,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that guy's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it fell into the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:35.02,Phone Lable,,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the keys are messed up, so I can't send a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind your phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What surprises me is you having a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hit you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really gotta ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said come in this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the front door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:56.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... it'd be better for me if \Nthey entered through the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sayin' they're yer friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.09,Facewriting 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawa—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was suspected of tryin' to kidnap \Na child in broad daylight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so they lectured him good at the village meetin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But every time folks gather, \Nit turns into a drinkin' party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.84,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:28.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been... so very worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:31.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A city boy like you, living in such a rural area...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're crying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:37.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so, so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You care that much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Friend, Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Friend, Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Friend Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you ignore my calls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fake?! A false friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! My cell phone's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! Find some other way to reach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:04.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I thought you'd be able to make it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You forget how inconvenient the countryside is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you throwing up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it tough coming here from Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With layovers, the flight took about three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. I don't know much about flying on planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't been on one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you guys ever been to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:28.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:30.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to Hyougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we're outta konomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:36.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Go get more"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can order your elders around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yer house, so what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You all get along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.33,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle schoolers these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It don't seem like yer a friend of Sensei's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just taggin' along with the drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply had to meet Handa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.91,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(346,40)}Kanzaki Kousuke
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki Kousuke, calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.49,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a card, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose this career because of \Nmy admiration for Handa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.66,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you look awfully young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:06.38,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! Me, too! Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I often get mistaken for a middle schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.67,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.03,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,An eighteen-year-old calligrapher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.34,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like I've heard that somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:16.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I worked up my courage and \Nentered the same competition as Handa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Tokyo Kasho Exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so clueless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up taking grand prize from the one I admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:31.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had always thought of Handa-san as above the \Nclouds, but he suddenly felt a lot closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe Handa-san just \Nwasn't really trying that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he talking about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From the mochi-gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second-Place Calligraphy Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a guy like that doin', \Ncomin' to meet Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause he wanted to see him lookin' mortified?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sensei were to learn his identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this enough konomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Handa-san, here's my card—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "No"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we always eat this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't mean the amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, that's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hooked on the stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san, you certainly are a funny one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:06.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he found out he lost \Nto such an obnoxious guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:12.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's got so much pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He could end up killing himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-san, in that recent calli—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, look how late it is already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You better get goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer stayin' at an inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed at the campground last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! Then you better \Nhead back to the campin' village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The road's dangerous at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji's asleep anyway, \Nso just spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.84,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated the campground. There were so many bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a lot I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.25,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's rarin' to spend the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to spend the night, \Ntoo, and hold him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.94,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got a college advisin' session tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:47.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any friend of Sensei's is a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.48,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I got club myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What've you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaah! My precious shield bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep weird pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, don't! If you excite them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to warn ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:18.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:18.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Usin' this, you can catch 'em \Nbefore they let off stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure know some \Ndicey underhanded tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It came in real handy here, \Nso don't call it "dicey."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.33,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, you really should leave for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The stink'll be attractin' other bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.12,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Handa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I... call you "Sensei," too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.02,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Crisis averted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was Kanzaki Kousuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look at all like a calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But his nasty side kinda shows through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew who he was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.66,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}From: Kawafuji\NSub: Answer your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:19.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not acquainted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but Kawafuji sent me a text.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:27.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm bringing Kanzaki Kousuke, the kid who won \Ngrand prize in the calligraphy competition."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a bit quirky, so be ready."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"See," nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were thinkin' you'd be all upset about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not as if I'm unbothered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have some envy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel more at ease somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go catch the rest of the shield bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.10,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to barge in again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay with tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:03.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawafuji didn't come today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.74,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Bright Camping Village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a terrible hangover and can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the thing about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In whatever he does, he has bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.83,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking tea in this heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.60,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Black soy tea really is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kawafuji-san tell you anything about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how you won a grand prize \Nand let it go to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mean thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.62,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly admire you, Handa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.31,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a look at my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.31,Magazine 4,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduction to Calligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.31,Magazine 6,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet & Movement\NCalming the Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.31,Magazine 7,,0000,0000,0000,,Modern Culture
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.31,Magazine 8,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide to Calligraphy                                                     Heart of Calligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up every book I could \Nfind that had you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:44.49,Magazine 9,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduction to\NCalligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:44.49,Magazine 10,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide to \NCalligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:44.49,Magazine 11,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet & Movement\NCalming the Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius calligrapher with \Na calligraphy expert as your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:44.49,Magazine 12,,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud\NMagazine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:44.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In every single book, your calligraphy is considered \Nbeautiful and faithful to the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See your smug face in this pin-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:49.41,Magazine 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Calligrapher\N{\fs18}Handa Seishuu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.41,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't make an expression \Nlike that without self-confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's one of you in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.04,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going for the impression of black ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.92,Magazine 3,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa Seishuu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's extremely embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.58,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are who I aspire to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:05.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I especially treasure the comments that you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:11.26,MX Calligraphy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Cloud\N{\fs24}Spring Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:11.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"As I inhale deeply of the refined air, \NI address my paper and brush,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and they respond to me, affirmingly."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.97,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't read that out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"To me, calligraphy is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the act of luring myself into catharsis..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "karta-sushi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.40,Karta,,0000,0000,0000,,Karta
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.48,Karta,,0000,0000,0000,,Karta                                       Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:22.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't console me wordlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's even lovelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop The Humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.22,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:31.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's being mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.65,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to laugh at me, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hear your famous lines live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I even brought a voice recorder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a maniac?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And after seeing your entry at the Kasho \NExhibition, I knew I had to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.60,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here in the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the calligraphy you submitted to the exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,one that you wrote after coming to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:56.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to Tokyo with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, my head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.76,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to see Kanzaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.49,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He 'round?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he went to Handa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.08,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:22.14,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to warn him not to \Nsay anything unnecessary to Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun looking after an adult, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.72,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't particularly lookin' after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite appearances, the guy's a real handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good without somebody \Nsupporting him from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:46.53,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Handa and I have been friends since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been bad at social interactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.70,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you some kind of idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.32,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime he opened his mouth, \Nhe'd say something high-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.11,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:56.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd get depressed easily, and wall himself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.16,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.79,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he even went and \Npunched a gallery director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been tough covering for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it I can picture his school days so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'd pictured the countryside as a place \Nwhere associating with others was important,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.93,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed that he'd give up \Nand come back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be having a lot of fun, living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you look after him a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya know Sensei so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.23,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,why'd ya come bringin' Kanzaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:29.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was feelin' mighty down after \Nlosin' the grand prize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:30.90,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My head again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.91,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fake sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:36.20,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an art dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before being my friend, Handa's a money tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Money tree"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.38,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be in trouble if he doesn't \Nproduce good works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he came to this island, \Nhe's been searching for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's probably floundering, \Nnot knowing what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for a person to mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,don't they need a rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.43,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.85,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a hangover, so I'll spend the day sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Handa I'm coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He does seem like you'd expect \Na friend of Sensei's to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lions smack their own cubs down into valleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.07,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, how does calligraphy \Nhave winners and losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.66,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a martial art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:20.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to Tokyo, and do calligraphy \Nseriously again, like you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:25.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this island to boost \Nmy skill in calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back until I get results.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Results...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:30.70,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What "results" are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.64,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd done calligraphy since grade school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:41.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but since it was just boring practice \Nday after day, I was planning to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.94,MX Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ward Residents Art Center
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.94,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I reluctantly visited a calligraphy exhibition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and saw calligraphy you had written.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.74,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"What pretty calligraphy!" I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:57.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you're not getting results.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:58.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:04.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're pointlessly attempting \Nto add too much individuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your writing is just forceful. \NIt's not like you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you lost to me is proof of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.69,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I expected you to feel mortified,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.63,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have no idea how \Nmuch you're degenerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This environment is ruining you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.35,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing calligraphy people will \Nacknowledge is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.52,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Your calligraphy is just plain dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:31.28,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,For one still so young, \Nyour calligraphy is highly conformist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.82,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,...better described as copybook-style...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.83,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.83,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even attempt to scale \Nthe wall of mediocrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.45,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of fussin' over that stuff, \NI'd rather have fun writin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.45,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.33,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stay in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.78,MX Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledged? By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.29,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sen—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:45.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.92,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I win a prize, but get told it's dull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.67,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I write good calligraphy, but don't win a prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:18:00.30,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the correct answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.56,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper airplanes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.52,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your planes really fly great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They fly when the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.29,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer flyin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.37,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing around, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something, Sense—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.13,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.87,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My calligraphy that you call pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.54,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is well-behaved calligraphy, \Nwritten the way my dad told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.80,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.39,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.81,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to write calligraphy only Handa Seishuu can write.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.05,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the correct answer is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.09,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but letting your words goad me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:57.03,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,into returning to Tokyo feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.40,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:01.50,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.77,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.83,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead and wait for me a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.55,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up right away, riding on the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.00,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.68,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you repeat those words once m—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:23.51,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.26,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a better hit than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naru, go call the village chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.78,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, you go get ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.44,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still got some growing up to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.16,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.24,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's this guy at our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.18,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:54.11,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Havin' a young man visit gives your \Nmother a reason to cook dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old hags shouldn't try for sex appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.21,MX Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna knock yer block off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.21,translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Translation: I'll hit you hard enough to dislocate your jaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.88,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's right, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.99,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, Naru was distributin' these \Nmagazines throughout the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.02,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yer real famous, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.27,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.95,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please autograph this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:17.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your mother have a grudge against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.48,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.19,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way he'd have an autogra—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.15,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.28,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... you said she was distributing \Nthem throughout the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.59,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we saw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.19,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.73,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These books're from a bookstore in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.34,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.71,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a real big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.17,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't got a signboard, so sign my T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.46,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't called Sensei for nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:41.42,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, calligraphy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.47,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I inhale deeply of the refined air...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.96,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.84,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luring myself into catharsis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.06,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.98,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:23.57,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:25.86,Man1,,0000,0000,0000,,Man 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.86,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep weird pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:30.45,Man2,,0000,0000,0000,,Man 2            Man 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:26.82,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:27.61,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:27.61,Man3,,0000,0000,0000,,Man 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.01,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.45,Man4,,0000,0000,0000,,Man 4            Man 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:30.45,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.75,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiroshi! Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:35.36,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.21,MX Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, is it okay to let go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:43.63,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Their army...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.51,MX Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,is increasin'!
